Pointing estimation system
Kosei Moriyama <cou929@gmail.com>

Description
===========
This system estimates direction of human's pointing gesture using range camera.
And display a mark onto estimated position using projector.

Usage
=====
% Make
% ./setSR
% ./pointEstimator

Files
=====
setSR		: Change permittion of video devices. Must be called once first of all.
src/		: Source files of this project.
include/	: Include files of this project.
data/		: Configuration data.